<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Музыкальный магазин</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="container mt-4">
<h1>Музыкальный магазин - GUI</h1>
<hr>

<h3>1. Количество произведений ансамбля</h3>
<form method="POST" action="/ensemble/compositions">
    <input type="number" name="ensembleId" placeholder="ID ансамбля" required class="form-control mb-2">
    <button class="btn btn-primary">Показать</button>
</form>

<h3>2. Пластинки ансамбля</h3>
<form method="POST" action="/ensemble/records">
    <input type="number" name="ensembleId" placeholder="ID ансамбля" required class="form-control mb-2">
    <button class="btn btn-primary">Показать</button>
</form>

<h3>3. Лидеры продаж</h3>
<a href="/bestsellers" class="btn btn-success">Показать</a>

<h3>4. Добавить пластинку</h3>
<form method="POST" action="/record/add">
    <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="Название" required class="form-control mb-2">
    <input type="number" name="price" placeholder="Цена" required class="form-control mb-2">
    <input type="number" name="stock" placeholder="На складе" required class="form-control mb-2">
    <button class="btn btn-warning">Добавить</button>
</form>

<h3>5. Добавить ансамбль</h3>
<form method="POST" action="/ensemble/add">
    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Название ансамбля" required class="form-control mb-2">
    <input type="text" name="type" placeholder="Тип" required class="form-control mb-2">
    <button class="btn btn-info">Добавить</button>
</form>
</body>
</html>
